OL,6,FA jury presiding in a trial concerning
OL,7,Fa Belfast man accused of murdering his
OL,8,Fwife was discharged on Tuesday.
OL,10,FA hearing into the August 2020 killing
OL,11,Fof mother-of-four Susan Baird was
OL,12,Fopened to a jury of five men and seven
OL,13,Fwomen at Belfast Crown Court women
OL,14,Flast week.
OL,16,FThe 60-year-old died as a result
OL,17,Fcatastrophic head injuries in the
OL,18,FWindermere Road home she shared with
OL,19,Fher husband Gary.
