OL,6,FThe 64-year old former BBC security
OL,7,Fguard has admitted attacking his wife
OL,8,Fwith a hammer in their Four Winds home.
OL,10,FHe has pleaded guilty to a charge of
OL,11,Fmanslaughter but this plea was not
OL,12,Faccepted by the prosecution.
OL,14,FAs the murder trial was due to enter
OL,15,Fits second week, a legal issue arose
OL,16,Fwhich was dealt with in the absence of
OL,17,Fthe jury.
