OL,6,FAfter making a ruling on the legal
OL,7,Fissue, trial judge Mr Justice
OL,8,FMcFarland determined that the jury
OL,9,Fshould be discharged.
OL,11,FThe 12 members were then brought back
OL,12,Fto court and were addressed by the
OL,13,Fsenior judge.
OL,15,FThanking them for their patience and
OL,16,Fissuing an apology, Mr Justice
OL,17,FMcFarland told them: "We have been
OL,18,Fdealing with a lot of issues in this
OL,19,Fcase, all day today, and the long and
OL,20,Fthe short of it is that we're not in a
OL,21,Fposition to proceed with the trial now.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G3/5
